  "keyFeatures": [
    "Code Splitting - Split code into bundles loaded on demand",
    "Loaders - Transform files during bundling (TypeScript, CSS, images, etc.)",
    "Plugins - Extensive plugin system for customization",
    "Hot Module Replacement - Update modules in browser without full reload",
    "Tree Shaking - Remove unused code for smaller bundles",
    "Module Federation - Share code between separate builds at runtime",
    "Optimization - Built-in code splitting, minification, and scope hoisting",
    "Asset Management - Handle images, fonts, and other assets",
    "Development Server - Built-in dev server with live reloading",
    "Multiple Module Formats - Support for ES modules, CommonJS, AMD"
